A rather intimidating knight astride a black horse.  He is clad in all black armour and his face shield is down.  He towers over you.
> speak to knight

> speak to knight
"Daisy Tunnelly at your service," you start politely.
"I arrest you for trespassing on Her Royal Majesty Princess Haifalutin's bridge crossing the River Branduin!"  Before you can say anything, he heaves you up onto his horse and gallops back over your bridge.  You gallop and gallop through unfamiliar woods until you come to an ancient castle.  He leaves you in the dungeon.  Apparently they take trespassing very seriously here!

You are in a Dungeon.
You can see a Guard, a Bread and a Water bowl.
