"Daisy Tunnelly at your service," you call up to the massive Ent.

"Ooom, hoom, a halfling," the Ent says, peering down at you.

"Excuse me please, but could you give me directions to Bree?" you ask politely.

"To Bree? No, halfling, I do not concern myself with the movements of men and halflings.  Hoom, boom.  I spend my days in loneliness here."

You suddenly remember the Entwife.  How will you signal her that you have found an Ent?
