You hand the tinderbox to the Ent.  "Oom, Hoom?" he inquires.

"Could you open this for me?" you ask, "It seems to be stuck."

The giant Ent crushes the box into a little pile of twisted metal, and hands you the flint that was inside.
> x flint

> x flint
A flint for making fires!
> use flint on firework

> use flint on firework
You strike the flint until you have lit the fuse of the firework.  The firework shoots into the air and explodes in a shower of sparkles.  Very very faintly you can hear an "Ooooommmm!" far in the distance.  "An Entwife!" the Ent exclaims.  He moves off towards the sound, revealing a trail that he had been blocking before.
> se

