You are in a Bree.
You are back in Bree!  Hip Hip Hooray!  As you run down the main street, your Tunnelly and Heathertoes relations swarm around you.  "We thought you were gone for good," they cry.  They drag you off to the Dancing Bear for a pint all round.  It is good to be home.
